snippet.title: (Download v0.1.1c) Project Reignition - SAGE 2024 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
This demo contains all the stages from Sand Oasis and Dinosaur Jungle. It also contains various skills.
====================
DOWNLOAD (v0.1.1c):
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1xTlQUe0-5CsxfGOZ1AcykDPrDGjOroWJ/view?usp=sharing
Mirror:
https://mega.nz/file/LDImVZ4R#Z1lG6Jy4bO3q_4PA9VipeAgjUmOSK86XCdPiNfdf2IY
Linux/Steam Deck Version:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1OQpnue1Rqmx7Npy6mk4hMw78N5f6apS4/view?usp=sharing
SAGE 2024 Booth:
https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/project-reignition-sage-2024-demo.2179/

Trailer edited by:
https://www.youtube.com/@UCMQjxeszhfJsWAd-jQwRGnA 
Trailer Music:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6IVCOCL5BCU
The Wicked Wild - Sonic and the Secret Rings Original Soundtrack

Please let me know if the download link is down or broken.
====================
Project Reignition is a fan recreation of Sonic and the Secret Rings. Project Reignition is not affiliated with SEGA in any way. All rights go to their respective owners.
